**2. Widget Search** (1 hour testing + fixes)
- [ ] Search with special characters (e.g., "C++") - verify regex doesn't crash
- [ ] Arrow down past last widget - verify stays at bottom (no wrap)
- [ ] Arrow up at first widget - verify stays at top (no wrap)
- [ ] Enter on empty search - verify no crash
- [ ] ESC clears search and refocuses - verify works
- [ ] Auto-focus when switching to Available tab - verify works
- [ ] Highlighting with multi-word search - verify all words highlighted
- [ ] Category filter + search combo - verify selectedIndex resets
- [ ] Dark mode highlighting readability - verify contrast
- **Expected Bugs:** Regex escaping edge cases, highlighting performance

**3. Calendar Print** (1 hour testing + fixes)
- [ ] Print from week view - verify layout fits landscape page
- [ ] Print from month view - verify all dates visible
- [ ] Print with many events - verify not cut off
- [ ] Print from dark mode - verify black/white output
- [ ] Print button hidden in print preview - verify
- [ ] Navigation/sidebar hidden in print - verify
- [ ] Events with long titles - verify word wrap works
- [ ] Print with no events - verify clean empty calendar
- [ ] Browser print preview (Ctrl+P) - verify matches print button
- **Expected Bugs:** Dark mode color leakage, layout overflow

