## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Severity | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|------------|
| Phase A uncovers critical bugs | High | Medium | Allocate 2h buffer for complex fixes |
| Phase B scope creep (too many features) | Medium | High | Stick to 5 core features, defer extras to Phase 2 |
| Phase C takes longer than estimated | Low | Medium | Prioritize critical docs (Feature Map, Implementation Plan) |
| Bundle size exceeds 50 KB in Phase B | Medium | Medium | Use lazy loading for heavy components |
| Testing reveals UX issues requiring redesign | High | Low | Focus on polish, not redesign (defer major UX to future sprint) |

